title: Koko wa Ore ni Makasete Saki ni Ike to Itte kara 10 Nen ga Tattara Densetsu ni Natteita
description: The Hero’s party was attacked by a large group of powerful devils. The party will no doubt be annihilated if this were to go on.One member of the party, the strongest mage, Rakku, decided to stop the enemies in the rift so the rest of his party could retreat and they and the world would survive...though it was obvious he wouldn't.But 10 years later, who's this young guy with the same name?
